      "updated": 1775505049716,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Registry policy\n    - deny all\n    - allow: docker.io, ghcr.io, quay.io\n\nContainer.conf defaults\n    - no_new_privileges\n    - default capabilities\n    - pids_limit = 4096\n    - default_ulimits \n    - bridge network\n    - Masked devices, diskstats, partitions\n",
      "fontSize": 14.336976092118817,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Registry policy\n    - deny all\n    - allow: docker.io, ghcr.io, quay.io\n\nContainer.conf defaults\n    - no_new_privileges\n    - default capabilities\n    - pids_limit = 4096\n    - default_ulimits \n    - bridge network\n    - Masked devices, diskstats, partitions\n",
